<p><strong>The Doctor's Dilemma</strong><br />
<strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1605736598" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;">Lt Flops</a></span></p>
<p>Written for the <strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/art-exchange-hub" target="_blank">7th Annual Holiday Art Exchange</a></strong> for <strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3213383); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3213383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1605736598" alt="OthellotheCat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3213383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3213383); return false;">OthellotheCat</a></span></strong>, who requested a piece featuring his characters!</p>
<p>This article is set in the <strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/end-of-death-hub" target="_blank">End of Death</a></strong> canon and features characters <strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/populated-control-led" target="_blank">Dr. Violet Mesmur</a></strong> and <strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3774" target="_blank">Leslie</a></strong>.</p>
